News.headline: Jordan Maguire-Drew Extends Loan Deal
News.short_description: The Daggers are delighted to announce that winger Jordan Maguire-Drew has extended his loan with the club until the end of the season
News.description:
Wide player Jordan Maguire-Drew has today extended his loan with the Daggers until 14th May 2017.

Jordan Maguire-Drew joined the Daggers in July 2016 and so far this season has made 30 appearances for the club getting nine goals and seven assists.
